POST	/api/market/items	发布新的二手商品:
示例请求体：
{
  "title": "Desk Chair",
  "description": "Comfortable and sturdy.",
  "price": 50.00,
  "category": "furniture",
  "images": ["http://chair1.jpg", "http://chair2.jpg"]
}
需要返回的格式：
{
  "itemId": "uuid-string",
  "title": "Desk Chair",
  "description": "Comfortable and sturdy.",
  "price": 50.00,
  "sellerId": "uuid-string",
  "createdAt": "timestamp",
  "status": "available",
  "images": ["http://chair1.jpg", "http://chair2.jpg"],
  "category": "furniture",
  "views": 0
}